trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> objects.
The CodeNamespaceImportCollection class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport> objects.
